schema.title: redsea
schema.description: Array of RDS groups from redsea

gap.description: Number of groups between successive 8A groups

delay_time.description: Position of the start of the activity/window sequence, referenced from the minute's edge, in seconds

activity_time.description: The time in a time slot during which 8A groups may be transmitted (seconds)

window_time.description: The time in a time slot during which transmission of 8A groups is suspended (seconds)

direction.description: Whether this event affects only one direction

extent.description: The event affects this many points from location

location.description: Location code (reference to a location database)

encrypted_location.description: Location code in its encrypted form

event_codes.description: Event codes (references to event code list)

update_class.description: Message replaces previous messages of this class

callsign.description: Call sign letters for a North American (RBDS) station

callsign_uncertain.description: Call sign letters for a North American (RBDS) station - probably erroneous due to a TMC workaround

channel.description: Which channel of a multi-channel signal this group was received on

prog_item_number.description: A numeric identifier for the currently running program

bler.description: Block Error Rate (averaged percentage of erroneous blocks)

oda_group.description: The group that carries this Open Data Application

clock_time.description: Time and date at transmitter (formatted to RFC 3339, section 5.6)

in_house_data.description: The contents of these bits are defined by the operator

other_network.description: Information about programs on other networks

prog_item_number.description: A numeric identifier for the currently running program
